    "60703860": {
      "title": "Combinatorial bounds on authentication codes with arbitration",
      "abstract": "Unconditionallysecure authentication codes with arbitration ( A2-codes)protect against deceptions from the transmitter and the receiveras well as that from the opponent. In this paper, we presentcombinatorial lower bounds on the cheating probabilities andthe sizes of keys of A2-codes. These bounds areall tight. Our main technique is a reduction of an A2-codeto a splitting A-code."
